author: mcooper
msg: TRINIDAD-2036 While ResourceServlet references files of type "ico", they won't load because CoreRenderKitResourceLoader doesn't register them
Added "ico" to the list of file types that CoreRenderKitResourceLoader registers (e.g. added to the list that includes ".css", ".cur", ".jpg", ".gif", ".png", ".jpeg", ".svg", and ".js").
